{"tid":554140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"火爆的哥殺上紅van搗亂毆司機","createTime":"2018-02-08T08:21:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-16T09:40:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"96da45ddda2d753089bdd466ada4e163c473c4c1","tid":554140,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T08:21:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180208/20298861\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180208%2F20298861&d=%2FhX2HLq%2BMhUlGVxEIFXTI8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=13d964b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180208%2F20298861&h=7964e1e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180208/20298861</a><br />\n<br />\n火爆的哥殺上紅van搗亂毆司機<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n【本報訊】一名狂躁的士司機，昨午駕車至旺角太子道西與一輛小巴相撞，他將怒氣發洩小巴司機身上，先衝入車內踢門扯扶手及拳毆司機，其後再取千斤頂狂扑小巴車身洩憤，警方到場調查以涉嫌襲擊及刑漽拘捕的士司機。肇事兩司機均報稱受傷，先後送院，的士司機候診時仍氣憤難平。<br />\n<br />\n現場為旺角太子道西近帝京酒店對開車路。昨早11時許，58歲姓陳男子駕駛一輛的士沿太子道西二線往深水埗方向，至上址時與鄰線一輛由50歲姓林司機駕駛的紅頂小巴相撞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180208/large/08la8p05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180208%2Flarge%2F08la8p05.jpg&h=6712d0e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【扯扶手跳窗】的士司機扯斷紅van車窗扶手後竟破窗而出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n送院後繼續鬧︰有心撞我<br />\n<br />\n根據目擊者提供短片，的士司機撞車後情緒激動，先衝入紅頂小巴大肆搗亂，起腳踢車門，再狂扯車窗扶手，將其扯斷後便由車窗跳落地下，他一度失衡跌坐路邊，其後再從的士車尾箱取出千斤頂，狂砸小巴車身，不斷爆粗高呼：「害我冇咗咁多錢喇！」有女途人勸阻：「唔好咁衝動啦叔叔，大家搵食箒！」但他未有理會繼續吵鬧，直至警方到場後才平復心情。<br />\n<br />\n警方在場調查期間，的士司機冷靜下來感後悔，一度欲走上救護車向小巴司機道歉，但被警員勸止，小巴司機報稱被人毆至頸痛，加上小巴損漽，警方以涉嫌刑漽及普通襲擊拘捕陳，他報稱頭痛與小巴司機同被送至廣華醫院治理，案件交由九龍城警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n陳送院後，躺在病床上候診期間承認曾出手，但仍對撞車事件憤憤不平：「嬲囉，佢有心撞我㗎！塞緊車，邊有人咁樣撞埋嚟㗎，『嘭』一聲撞埋嚟！」強調事發時先讓一輛小巴先行，然後打燈轉入鄰線，但被肇事小巴撞上，慨嘆萬多元「墊底費」泡湯，擔心「仲邊有咁多錢開車？」<br />\n<br />\n■記者梁澤岡<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180208/large/08la8p061.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180208%2Flarge%2F08la8p061.jpg&h=0a370e02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【千斤頂扑車】之後取出千斤頂狂砸小巴車身。"},{"pid":"5faa20a28f86979be0eeb5ba6829ad9ce83c19d8","tid":554140,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T08:24:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b511e5a8127bc0b1675a75d52d71785701adb348","tid":554140,"uid":154725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5faa20a28f86979be0eeb5ba6829ad9ce83c19d8","tid":554140,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T08:24:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T08:28:40.000Z","msg":"佢先打完人 再打車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n定係你話佢點解唔用千斤頂打爆小巴司機個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590034bf5d64da65b02c1c54dae6c5195d0ebb49","tid":554140,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T08:28:44.000Z","msg":"hulk smash"},{"pid":"568dc54fb8a3ecec6ec15c4e6f25a88a7c4d0d2a","tid":554140,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T08:30:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180208/large/08la8p05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180208%2Flarge%2F08la8p05.jpg&h=6712d0e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好有動感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24281b235cd08090a5ea5830228565ba14aca2e5","tid":554140,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"568dc54fb8a3ecec6ec15c4e6f25a88a7c4d0d2a","tid":554140,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T08:30:48.000